OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1784787486
OL,3,CMan who fled to Spain to avoid police
OL,4,Camong four jailed for supplying drugs
OL,6,FA British man who masterminded the
OL,7,Fsupply of drugs and illegal firearms
OL,8,Fworth millions of pounds has been
OL,9,Fjailed.
OL,11,FCraig Bennett, 41, worked with three
OL,12,Fother men from Berkshire to distribute
OL,13,Fcash, weapons and drugs, in what the
OL,14,FNCA describes as a large-scale
OL,15,Foperation.
OL,17,FHe was identified as a user of
OL,18,FEncrochat, an encrypted communications
OL,19,Fplatform used by criminals to
OL,20,Fcommunicate anonymously with each
OL,21,Fother under aliases, in 2020.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
