FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1784787486
OL,3,CMan who fled to Spain to avoid police
OL,4,Camong four jailed for supplying drugs
OL,6,FOfficers from the National Crime
OL,7,FAgency infiltrated the platform and
OL,8,Fused messages he sent to build a
OL,9,Fpicture of his criminality.
OL,11,FBennett directed couriers Gerald
OL,12,FTohill, 60, from Berkshire, and Lucien
OL,13,FRobinson, 38, from Wokingham to
OL,14,Fcollect and distribute illicit cash
OL,15,Fand drugs on numerous occasions.
OL,17,FLucien Robinson's father, 75-year-old
OL,18,FPeter Robinson from Berkshire, was
OL,19,Falso involved in hiding cash for the
OL,20,Fenterprise.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
