FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1784787486
OL,3,CMan who fled to Spain to avoid police
OL,4,Camong four jailed for supplying drugs
OL,6,FIn total the organised crime group
OL,7,Fwere linked to the supply of 91.8
OL,8,Fkilos of drugs with a street value of
OL,9,F#3.75m.
OL,11,FBennett was eventually arrested in
OL,12,FBarcelona in July 2025 during a
OL,13,FPolicia Nacional operation supported
OL,14,Fby National Crime Agency International
OL,15,FLiaison Officers, following their
OL,16,Finvestigations.
OL,18,FFollowing Bennett's arrest, he was
OL,19,Fextradited to the UK in August 2025.
OL,20,FThe other defendants were summoned to
OL,21,Fcourt as part of the process.
OL,26,@uD@Frt
