PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1784787486
OL,3,CMan who fled to Spain to avoid police
OL,4,Camong four jailed for supplying drugs
OL,6,FBennett, Peter Robinson and Lucien
OL,7,FRobinson pleaded guilty to their
OL,8,Foffences at Reading Crown Court in
OL,9,Flate 2025 with Tohill later convicted
OL,10,Fat trial. Peter Robinson was sentenced
OL,11,Fon 1 June with the three other men
OL,12,Fsentenced today (21 July) at the same
OL,13,Fcourt. Collectively they received 28
OL,14,Fyears.
OL,16,FNCA Senior Investigating Officer John
OL,17,FTurner, said: "Bennett was the
OL,18,Flinchpin of this conspiracy to bring
OL,19,Fharmful drugs into the UK as well as
OL,20,Fseeking access to potentially deadly
OL,21,Fweapons.
OL,26,@yD@OOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
