FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1784787486
OL,3,CMan who fled to Spain to avoid police
OL,4,Camong four jailed for supplying drugs
OL,6,F"He directed the movements of his co-
OL,7,Fconspirators, all of them benefiting
OL,8,Ffrom the damage they were inflicting
OL,9,Fto individuals in our communities.
OL,11,F"Criminals who used Encrochat believed
OL,12,Fthey were beyond the reach of the law,
OL,13,Fbut this case along with numerous
OL,14,Fothers proves otherwise.
OL,16,F"The NCA along with partners at home
OL,17,Fand abroad will continue to track down
OL,18,Fserious offenders and protect the
OL,19,Fpublic from their criminality."
